---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 518
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Salvation Through Faith
  - 542
By: Dhu ’l-Nûn
Description: Citing spiritual counsel given him by a stranger
---
Do not lose thy hope in God, even for the twinkling of an eye. Never
interrupt thy relations with God. and thou wilt find joy the day when
sinners are undone.
